    <title>opencv_cpp编译</title>
    <link href="https://cracknum.github.io/wiki/opencv-cpp%E7%BC%96%E8%AF%91/"/>
    <id>https://cracknum.github.io/wiki/opencv-cpp编译/</id>
    <published>2022-10-20T12:17:41.000Z</published>
    <updated>2022-10-20T14:12:54.327Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="环境">1. 环境</h2><blockquote><p><strong>操作系统</strong>: Windows11 21H2<br /><strong>CMake-gui</strong>: 3.24.2<font color=#f391a9>(不要使用3.25.0-rc2，在configure过车中会出现类型大小检查错误)</font><br /><strong>OpenCV</strong>: 4.6.0</p></blockquote><h2 id="编译过程">2. 编译过程</h2><h3 id="cmake使用流程">3.1 CMake使用流程</h3><ol type="1"><li>选择源码目录</li><li>选择编译存储目录</li><li>configure</li><li>generate <img src="2022-10-20-20-32-38.png" /></li></ol><h2 id="使用cmake-gui-3.25.0-rc2出现的错误">3.2使用CMake-gui-3.25.0-rc2出现的错误</h2><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">Check size of size_t</span><br><span class="line">CMake Error at C:/Users/赵磊/Downloads/cmake-3.25.0-rc2-windows-x86_64/share/cmake-3.25/Modules/CheckTypeSize.cmake:147 (try_compile):</span><br><span class="line">  Cannot copy output executable</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    &#x27;&#x27;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">  to destination specified by COPY_FILE:</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    &#x27;E:/opencv/tmp/CMakeFiles/CheckTypeSize/SIZEOF_SIZE_T.bin&#x27;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">  Recorded try_compile output location doesn&#x27;t exist:</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    E:/opencv/tmp/CMakeFiles/CMakeScratch/TryCompile-one8tx/Debug/cmTC_66609.exe</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">Call Stack (most recent call first):</span><br><span class="line">  C:/Users/赵磊/Downloads/cmake-3.25.0-rc2-windows-x86_64/share/cmake-3.25/Modules/CheckTypeSize.cmake:277 (__check_type_size_impl)</span><br><span class="line">  3rdparty/libjpeg-turbo/CMakeLists.txt:25 (check_type_size)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="使用vs编译cmake生成的目录文件">3.3使用VS编译CMake生成的目录文件</h3><ol type="1"><li><p>编译OpenCV项目（在ALL_BUILD右键生成）</p></li><li><p>生成安装文件（include, bin, lib，在INSTALL处右键生成）</p></li></ol><p><img src="2022-10-20-21-47-33.png" /></p><ol start="3" type="1"><li>完成上述步骤后，在build目录下就会出现install目录，在其中的一些目录就包含了include和x64(bin,lib)</li></ol><h3 id="在vs2022编译过程中出现的问题">3.4在VS2022编译过程中出现的问题</h3><blockquote><p>严重性 代码 说明 项目 文件 行 禁止显示状态 错误 C2059 语法错误:“)”opencv_test_objdetect D:-4.x_qrcode_encode.cpp 324 警告 C4819该文件包含不能在当前代码页(936)中表示的字符。请将该文件保存为 Unicode格式以防止数据丢失 opencv_test_objdetect D:-4.x_qrcode_encode.cpp1<br />错误 C2059 语法错误:“for” opencv_test_objdetect D:-4.x_qrcode_encode.cpp324 错误 C2143 语法错误: 缺少“)”(在“;”的前面) opencv_test_objdetectD:-4.x_qrcode_encode.cpp 324 错误 C2065 “i”: 未声明的标识符opencv_test_objdetect D:-4.x_qrcode_encode.cpp 324 错误 C2065 “i”:未声明的标识符 opencv_test_objdetect D:-4.x_qrcode_encode.cpp 324 错误C2275 “std::string”: 将此类型用作表达式非法 opencv_test_objdetectD:-4.x_qrcode_encode.cpp 326 错误 C2146 语法错误:缺少“)”(在标识符“input_info”的前面) opencv_test_objdetectD:-4.x_qrcode_encode.cpp 326 错误 C2065 “input_info”: 未声明的标识符opencv_test_objdetect D:-4.x_qrcode_encode.cpp 328 错误 C2065“input_info”: 未声明的标识符 opencv_test_objdetectD:-4.x_qrcode_encode.cpp 350 错误 C2737 “gtest_ar”: 必须初始化 const对象 opencv_test_objdetect D:-4.x_qrcode_encode.cpp 350 错误 C2059语法错误:“}” opencv_test_objdetect D:-4.x_qrcode_encode.cpp 435 错误C2143 语法错误: 缺少“;”(在“}”的前面) opencv_test_objdetectD:-4.x_qrcode_encode.cpp 435</p></blockquote><ul><li>解决方案参考<ahref="https://blog.csdn.net/pypyquixue/article/details/123448814">vs2022重新编译opencv-pythoncuda加速时报错</a></li></ul>]]></content>
    
